---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Ariff Mohamed - Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer | MIT Cybersecurity Student" description="Expert Azure cloud solutions engineer specializing in security, automation, and compliance. Showcasing enterprise Azure projects including PowerShell automation, KQL analytics, storage security, and Intune device management.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Ariff Mohamed</h1>
      <h2>Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer | Security Specialist</h2>
      <p>Transforming enterprise cloud infrastructure with security-first Azure architecture and innovative automation solutions. Currently advancing cybersecurity expertise at MIT.</p>
      <div class="hero-links">
        <a class="btn-primary" href="#projects">View Azure Projects</a>
        <a class="btn-secondary" href="#about">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Azure Projects Grid -->
  <section class="projects" id="projects">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Featured Azure Projects</h2>
      <p>Explore my specialized Azure implementations focused on automation, security, and enterprise management</p>
      
      <div class="projects-grid">
        <div class="project-card">
          <h3>Azure Automation Hub</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive PowerShell runbook automation platform for enterprise user management, resource provisioning, and operational workflows. Features advanced scheduling, error handling, and audit trails.</p>
          <a class="project-link" href="https://automation.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank">Explore Automation →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-card">
          <h3>Log Analytics Toolkit</h3>
          <p>Advanced KQL query library and monitoring dashboard suite for Azure security insights, performance analysis, and compliance reporting. Real-time alerting and custom workbooks included.</p>
          <a class="project-link" href="https://log.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank">Explore Analytics →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-card">
          <h3>Secure Storage Patterns</h3>
          <p>Enterprise-grade Azure storage security implementations featuring encryption at rest and in transit, compliance frameworks, access policies, and data governance best practices.</p>
          <a class="project-link" href="https://storage.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank">Explore Storage →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-card">
          <h3>Device Compliance Monitor</h3>
          <p>Microsoft Intune-powered device management and compliance monitoring solution. Automated policy enforcement, security baselines, and comprehensive reporting for enterprise endpoints.</p>
          <a class="project-link" href="https://compliance.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank">Explore Compliance →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Side Projects Section -->
  <section class="side-projects" id="side-projects">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Side Projects</h2>
      <p>Personal development tools and experimental applications</p>
      
      <div class="projects-grid">
        <div class="project-card secondary">
          <h3>Todo Application</h3>
          <p>A modern, responsive task management application built with modern web technologies. Features task organization, priority management, and progress tracking.</p>
          <a class="project-link" href="https://todo.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank">Try Todo App →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>As an Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer specializing in security architecture, I bring deep technical expertise in enterprise cloud infrastructure, automation, and compliance. My experience spans large-scale Azure implementations, security frameworks, and innovative problem-solving for complex business challenges.</p>
          
          <p>Currently advancing my expertise through MIT's Cybersecurity program, I'm passionate about developing secure, scalable Azure solutions that drive business value while maintaining the highest security and compliance standards.</p>
          
          <div class="expertise">
            <h3>Azure Specializations</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Azure Security Architecture</li>
              <li>PowerShell Automation & Runbooks</li>
              <li>KQL & Log Analytics</li>
              <li>Microsoft Intune Management</li>
              <li>Storage Security & Encryption</li>
              <li>Compliance & Governance</li>
              <li>Identity & Access Management</li>
              <li>DevSecOps Implementation</li>
              <li>Threat Detection & Response</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
      <p>Interested in collaborating on Azure cloud security solutions or discussing enterprise automation projects? Let's connect.</p>
      
      <div class="contact-links">
        <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:ariff@aglobaltec.com">
          <span>Email</span>
          <span>ariff@aglobaltec.com</span>
        </a>
        
        <a class="contact-link" href="https://linkedin.com/in/ariff-afandi" target="_blank">
          <span>LinkedIn</span>
          <span>Professional Profile</span>
        </a>
        
        <a class="contact-link" href="https://github.com/a-ariff" target="_blank">
          <span>GitHub</span>
          <span>Technical Portfolio</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0078d4 0%, #005a9e 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 100px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .hero-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  
  .hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  
  .hero-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: white;
    color: #0078d4;
  }
  
  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid white;
  }
  
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: white;
    color: #0078d4;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  
  .projects, .side-projects {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }

  .side-projects {
    background: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .projects h2, .side-projects h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #333;
  }
  
  .projects > .container > p, .side-projects > .container > p {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .projects-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .project-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .project-card.secondary {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
  }
  
  .project-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }
  
  .project-card h3 {
    color: #0078d4;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .project-card.secondary h3 {
    color: #6c757d;
  }
  
  .project-card p {
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .project-link {
    color: #0078d4;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .project-card.secondary .project-link {
    color: #6c757d;
  }
  
  .project-link:hover {
    color: #005a9e;
  }

  .project-card.secondary .project-link:hover {
    color: #495057;
  }
  
  .about {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: white;
  }
  
  .about h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #333;
  }
  
  .about-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .expertise {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  
  .expertise h3 {
    color: #0078d4;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  
  .expertise ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .expertise li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: #555;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .expertise li:before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #0078d4;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  
  .contact {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }
  
  .contact h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #333;
  }
  
  .contact > .container > p {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .contact-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .contact-link {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    display: block;
  }
  
  .contact-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }
  
  .contact-link span:first-child {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0078d4;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .contact-link span:last-child {
    color: #666;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .hero-links {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .projects-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .expertise ul {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
